@startuml
skin rose
title 运营后台设置库存（单条原子更新）
actor 运营人员 as Admin
participant "运营后台" as Backoffice
participant "库存服务" as StockSvc

Admin -> Backoffice: 设置可售库存( skuId, channel, newAvailable )
Backoffice -> StockSvc: 调整库存请求( requestId, skuId, channel, newAvailable )
activate StockSvc
note right of StockSvc
核心DB操作(同事务):
- UPDATE trade_pd_stock SET sq = lq + oq + newAvailable
- INSERT trade_pd_stock_log(order_action=OrderActionEnum.ADJUST)
end note
StockSvc --> Backoffice: 调整成功
deactivate StockSvc
@enduml